ave|first= Robert L.|others=University of California, Berkeley. Center for South and Southeast Asia Studies|edition=|publisher=University of California Press |year=1969|location=Los Angeles |ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book |last=Hunter|first=Sir William Wilson |title=Imperial Gazetteer of India Vol. XXII Singbhum to Trashi-Chod-Zong |year=1908 |publisher=Clarendon Press |location=Oxford |isbn=|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=635DAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA373&dq=tinnevelly+imperial+hunter|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GG06ImmHy1oC&pg=PA111&dq=tirunelveli+schools |title=The Violence of Development: The Political Economy of Gender |last= Kapadia |first= Karin |edition=|publisher=Kali for Women 2002 |year=2002 |isbn=1842772074 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NE5UKHOFVGYC&pg=PA76&dq=tirunelveli |title=Human rights violation |last= Kanmony |first= Jebagnanam Cyril  |edition=|publisher= |year=2010 |isbn=81-8324-347-9 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-BcUujyJpKEC&pg=PA114&dq=tirunelveli+economy |title=5. Essays on Indian Economy |last= Kumar |first= Raj |edition=|publisher=Discovery Publishing House |year=2003 |isbn=81-7141-700-0 |ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book |last=Kumar |first=Sehdev |authorlink= |title= A thousand petalled lotus: Jain temples of Rajasthan : architecture & iconography|year=2001|publisher=Indra Gandhi National Centre of Arts|location=New Delhi |isbn=81-7017-348-5|ref=harv}}.\n* {{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=boYncPEOJwcC&pg=PA121&dq=tirunelveli+schools |title=Christianity Reborn: The Global Expansion of Evangelicalism in the Twentieth Century|last= Lewis |first= Donald M. |edition=|publisher=Wm. B. Eerdmans Publishing Co. |year=2004 |isbn=0-8028-2483-8 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CBNMY34zknIC&pg=PA2&dq=tirunelveli+schools |title=Indian English Women's FictionA Study of Marriage, Career And Divorce|last= Manohar |fi