ostlier by Rs 8\u201310 lakh per MW|work =The Economic Times|date=26 July 2012|accessdate=22 December 2012|ref={{sfnRef|''The Economic Times''|26 July 2012}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.in/2003/02/27/stories/2003022701330800.htm |title=Suryan FM gets ready to turn the radios on|work =Business Line|date=26 February 2003|accessdate=22 December 2012|ref={{sfnRef|''Business Line''|26 February 2003}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2011/04/21/stories/2011042157080500.htm |title=Court says \u2018no' to use of \u2018Iruttukadai'|work =The Hindu|date=21 April 2011|accessdate=22 December 2012|ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|21 April 2011}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/arts/magazine/article3554551.ece |title=In search of Srivilliputtur Palgova|work =The Hindu|date=23 June 2012|accessdate=22 December 2012|ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|23 June 2012}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-tamilnadu/six-lakh-passports-issued-in-five-years/article4177360.ece |title=Six lakh passports issued in five years|work =The Hindu|date=8 December 2012|accessdate=17 January 2007|ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|8 December 2012}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2007/01/17/stories/2007011716060300.htm |title=Fun science gallery inaugurated in Tirunelveli|work =The Hindu|date=17 January 2007|accessdate=17 January 2007|ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|17 January 2007}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2007/01/10/stories/2007011004360200.htm |title=Tamil Nadu / Tirunelveli News : Anna Stadium to get floodlight facility |work=The Hindu |date=10 January 2007 |accessdate=2012-10-19|ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|10 January 2007}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-tamilnadu/article3565107.ece |title= Government expo to begin on June 29 |work=The Hindu |date=24 June 2012 |accessdate=29 December 2012|ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|24 June 2012}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/karunanidhi-puts-tata-project-on-hold/207767/ |title=Karunanidhi puts Tata project on hold \u2013 Indian Express|date=31 July 2007|accessdate=18 December 2012|work=The Indian Express|ref={{sfnRef|''The Indian Express''|31 July 2007}}}}\n* {{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2007/05/19/stories/2007051909370400.htm |title=400 years sugar cane press|ref={{sfnRef|''The Hindu''|19 May 2007}}|date=19 May 2007|accessdate=18 December 2012|work=The Hindu}}\n* {{cite news|title=AIADMK\u2019s Bhuvaneswari set to become Tirunelveli mayor|last=M.|first=Aruloli|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/140909/nation-politics/article/aiadmk%E2%80%99s-bhuvaneswari-set-become-tirunelveli-mayor|accessdate=28 October 2014|work=Deccan Chronicle|date=9 September 2014|ref={{sfnRef|''Deccan Chronicle''|9 September 2014}}}}\n* {{cite web|title=Census Info 2011 Final population totals|url=http://www.censusindia.gov.in/2011census/censusinfodashboard/index.html|publisher=Office of The Registrar General and Census Commissioner, Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India|year=2013|accessdate=26 Jan 2014|ref={{sfnRef|Census dashboard|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web|title=Census Info 2011 Final population totals \u2013 Tirunelveli|url=http://www.censusindia.gov.in/pca/SearchDetails.aspx?Id=701597|publisher=Office of The Registrar General and Census Commissioner, Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India|year=2013|accessdate=26 Jan 2014|ref={{sfnRef|Census of India|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web|title=Population By Religious Community - Tamil Nadu|year=2011|url=http://www.censusindia.gov.in/2011census/C-01.html|format=XLS|publisher=Office of The Registrar General and Census Commissioner, Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India|accessdate=13 September 2015|ref={{sfnRef|Religious census|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web|title=Nellai Medical College|url=http://www.nellaimedicos.com/|publisher=Nellai Medical College|accessdate=29 December 2012|ref={{sfnRef|Nellai Medical College}}}}\n* {{cite web|title=Veterina