|2011}} }}\n* {{cite web|title=Commissionerate of Municipal Administration|url=http://www.tn.gov.in/cma/chart5.htm|publisher=Commissionerate of Municipal Administration|accessdate = 26 June 2012|year=2006|ref={{sfnRef|Commissionerate of Municipal Administration|2006}} }}\n* {{cite web|title=Parliamentary constituency map|url=http://ceotamilnadu.nic.in/forms/int3.pdf|format=PDF|publisher=Chief Election Officer\u2013 Tamil Nadu|accessdate=8 June 2012|page=9|year=2000|ref={{sfnRef|Parliamentary constituency map|2008}}|url-status=dead|archiveurl=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20090619072255/http%3A//ceotamilnadu.nic.in/forms/int3.pdf|archivedate=19 June 2009|df=dmy-all}}\n* {{cite web|title=Primary census abstract 2001|url=http://census2001.tn.nic.in/pca2001.aspx|publisher=Directorate of Census Operations &nbsp;\u2013 Tamil Nadu|accessdate=8 June 2012|year=2001|ref={{sfnRef|Census of India|2001}}|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110217153857/http://census2001.tn.nic.in/pca2001.aspx|archivedate=17 February 2011|df=dmy-all}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.fallingrain.com/world/IN/25/Tirunelveli.html|title= Falling Rain Genomics, Inc \u2013 Tirunelveli|publisher=Falling Rain Genomics Inc|ref={{sfnRef|Falling Rain Genomics}}}}\n* {{cite web\n| url = http://www.vismuseum.org.in/units.html\n| title = Visvesvaraya Industrial & Technological Museum Bangalore India: Satellite Units\n| accessdate = 14 October 2008\n|ref={{sfnRef| Visvesvaraya Satellite Centre}}\n}}\n* {{cite web|author=Tirunelveli Corporation |url=http://210.212.242.69/?page_id=10|year=2011 |title= Tirunelveli Corporation |publisher=210.212.242.69 |accessdate=29 December 2012|ref={{sfnRef|About Corporation|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://eci.nic.in/eci_main/electionanalysis/AE/S22/partycomp218.htm|title=Partywise Comparison Since 1977|publisher=Election Commission of India|accessdate=16 April 2011|ref={{sfnRef|Partywise Comparison Since 1977|2011}}}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://eci.nic.in/eci_